## Project Summary

`web-crm` is a full-featured CRM web app with ERP placeholder modules. It uses Node.js native `http`, built-in `node:sqlite`, and a vanilla HTML/CSS/JS frontend. There is no build step.

Important constraint: use built-in `node:sqlite` with `DatabaseSync`. Do not migrate to or suggest `better-sqlite3`; the local machine may not compile native addons.

